rsion": "1.0", "version_code": 180, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "7473971379394072"}, "asset_files": {"count": 5}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "4963431797114722", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "7474016142722929"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "247209914665124"}]}, "change_log": "Patch 1.2.0.1\nPrevent body leaning while looking down.\nIncreased foot step attenuation radius by a little.\nAdjust armor body location, so it's easier to grab things when looking down.", "created_date": 1734768001, "id": "7462773067180570", "version": "1.0", "version_code": 179, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "7462734350517775"}, "asset_files": {"count": 5}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "4963431797114722", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "7474016142722929"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "247209914665124"}]}, "change_log": "ExfilZone Update Patch Notes\nNew Features:\n- Tutorial Area: Added a tutorial area accessible through the main menu.\n- Tactical Leaning: Implemented tactical leaning mechanics.\n- Backup Supply: Merchants now offer a low-cost, time-limited basic equipment set.\n- JOHNNY Merchant: Weekly high-value buybacks for specific items.\n- Armor & Helmet Settings: Added a setting to unequip armor and helmets using a combination key.\n- Audio Rework: Reworked weapon, footstep, and Metro audio attenuation.\n- Default Item Grab Sound: Added a default sound effect for grabbing items.\n- Locked Item Info: Clicking on locked items now displays the unlock conditions.\n- Performance: Increased Quest 2 performance compared to the Alpha Test version.\nNew Weapons and Magazines:\n- G3SG1 7.62x51 Assault Rifle\n- G3SG1 7.62x51 Mag (20-round)\nNew Headgear:\n- LH-250 Pilot Helmet\n- Tsh-4M Tank Helmet\nNew Body Armors:\n- 6B2 Body Armor\n- Press PACA Body Armor\n- Security PACA Body Armor\n- Police PACA Body Armor\n- 6B17 Body Armor\n- 6B17 Upgraded Body Armor\nNew Backpacks:\n- Robinson BFM Backpack\n- Odldos Flowers Backpack\n- Odldos Black Backpack\nAdjustments:\n- UI Visibility: Hunger, thirst, and carrying capacity now only display when their status changes.\n- Localization: Filled in missing translations for all languages.\n- Scavenger Mode: No longer inherits hideout health settings from Contractors mode.\n- Hideout Adjustments:\n  - Structural changes to Hideout layout.\n  - Ammo reloading and armor repair unavailable during power outages.\n- Food Interaction:\n  - Improved interaction experience.\n  - Food disappears after consumption (except refillable bottles).\n  - Faster recovery after consuming food.\n- Map Changes: Updated BR and EZ MICA maps, adjusted some mini-map location names.\n- Audio: Adjusted death sound effects.\n- Merchant UI: Improved display in the merchant purchase screen.\n- Delivery Kiosk UI: Enhanced Item Delivery Kiosk UI display.\n- Ammo Adjustments: Fixed incorrect collisions for 9x19 and .45 ACP bullets.\n- Weapon Stats: Added detailed attributes for weapons, ammo, and grenades.\nBalancing:\n- Hideout Facilities:\n  - Adjusted material requirements, prices, and levels.\n  - Reduced the quantity of some required materials.\n- Experience:\n  - Modified overall player experience progression.\n  - Adjusted experience required per level.\n- Loot Distribution: Rebalanced item distribution for better scavenging.\n- Shop Pricing:\n  - Adjusted weapon, attachment, and ammo prices.\n  - Modified recycling prices for certain items.\n- Boss Adjustments:\n  - Reduced boss spawn rates (no longer 100%).\n  - Tweaked police station boss equipment.\n- Item Unlocks:\n  - Revised unlock conditions for some items.\n  - Adjusted item exchange requirements.\n- Weapon Recoil: Reconfigured weapon recoil and attachment bonuses.\n- Armor Durability: Slightly reduced bullet damage to armor durability.\nBug Fixes:\n- Fixed Scav players spawning together.\n- Resolved issues caused by disconnections affecting equipment, missions, and friend lists.\n- Fixed duplication of equipment.\n- Addressed anomalies with removing items from junk boxes.\n- Fixed item refresh issues in the \"Sell\" interface.\n- Resolved truck marking issues in the \"Where Did The Trucks Go\" mission.\n- Fixed grenades colliding with UI and causing nearby explosions.\n- Corrected issues with unsellable items.\n- Fixed Sjogren shotgun slug spread behavior.\n- Resolved red dot sights' zeroing issues.\n- Adjusted PKP sight positioning with rail attachments.\n- Fixed overlapping items in ammo pouches and painkillers.\n- Addressed issues with storing and stacking certain items.\n- Corrected misspelled letters on the server room door sign.\n- Fixed hand texture issues in Hand-Only mode.\n- Resolved spacing inconsistencies between certain armor and holsters.\n- Fixed clipping issues with equipment worn by certain bots.\n- Addressed collision bugs with specific attachments in BR mode.\nMap Adjustments:\n- Resolved visual clipping issues across the map.\n- Fixed a bug causing players to get stuck near the Motel windows.\n- Addressed an issue where players could get trapped in rock crevices above the northern tunnel at the mall.\n- Corrected a clipping issue at the underground extraction point near the black market.\nEnvironment Fixes:\n- Fixed overly bright glass railings in the mall.\n- Resolved obstruction issues on the second-floor staircase of the office building near the motel.\n- Fixed a bug where players could get stuck after jumping off the cliff north of the dam.\n- Addressed an issue with players getting trapped on the outer wall fence of the police station in Hyder Town.\nPostponed Feature\nCustom Lobby for Battle Royale Mode:\nThe custom lobby feature for Battle Royale mode has been postponed to allow us to refine and optimize its functionality. We are working hard to make it available as soon as possible.", "created_date": 1734619221, "id": "7453514404773103", "version": "1.0", "version_code": 178, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "7453450508112826"}, "asset_files": {"count": 5}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "4963431797114722", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "7474016142722929"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1734177189, "id": "7424579714333239", "version": "1.0", "version_code": 177, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "7424518134339397"}, "asset_files": {"count": 5}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "4963431797114722", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "7474016142722929"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1734111199, "id": "7420345041423373", "version": "1.0", "version_code": 176, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "7420278798096664"}, "asset_files": {"count": 5}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}